title: [New Product Offering] - inSure NFTs
body:
As promised we have created inSure NFTs 
Please check: https://rarible.com/insuretoken

inSure NFT is a unique and rare proposition that both helps to grow the risk pool for inSure DeFi project and allows inSure NFT holders to have the protection of their crypto portfolios. 

This is a limited edition NFTs that include the insurance plan from inSure DeFi project (only 8 NFTs were issued)
The owner of this NFT will receive a crypto protection plan from drastic devaluations of crypto assets, scams, and stolen funds (exchange closures). The insurance plan will be calculated based on the purchase price of inSure NFT. 

We are also welcoming our community to contribute with NFT designs and receive royalties from the sale of NFTs!

If you have any ideas/questions, want to help with design work, please contact us via email: info@insuretoken.net or on Telegram: t.me/insureteam
